{
  "stem": "11274.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were four kilometers from us already there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So when we escaped-- that's right-- the hardships after they came was hard-- was not so difficult because it was a short distance only to the Czechoslovakian border.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that's how my sister escaped, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because it was so close with that little boy that she could escape, Zosia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But before you get into the escapes, let's talk about what happened when the Germans first came in your town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first day that they came in, they got themself a list, from the city, of the Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They picked one man-- they decided, by their decision-- to call-- to ask-- appoint as a Jewish elder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Joseph-- I don't want to use last names because-- [INAUDIBLE] use his name in the-- in the book, too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Joseph was appointed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They summoned Joseph to come-- to-- to come to the headquarters and give them a complete list of all the-- of all the young Jewish people, boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was forced to do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't volunteer work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So-- so else he would be shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then the Jewish girls got from a notification, after they had the names, they had to be-- they're assigned to their quarters, and there was some of them scrubbing floors, and some of them polishing boots, or everything, in one building if they weren't too many.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to go in the morning, go in there until they said, you can go home now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were working there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "No pay and no food, or nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Just slave labor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We started already there so, for the rest of it that came later, like Auschwitz, I had a little bit of preparation knowing what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
